query:
INSERT INTO history
                    (manga_id, created_at, updated_at, chapter_id, page, scroll, percent, chapters, deleted_at, user_id)
                VALUES
                    (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
                ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE
                    created_at = ?,
                    updated_at = ?,
                    chapter_id = ?,
                    page = ?,
                    scroll = ?,
                    percent = ?,
                    chapters = ?,
                    deleted_at = ?
